ECC Info





      View Menu
      
Down arrow icon
















            hours
          Heading link



 
Copy link



The Engineering Career Center offers in-person drop-in advising during the academic year. See our hours below.
ECC staff will continue to wear masks when meeting with students in person. All students are recommended and requested to wear a mask when visiting the Engineering Career Center, regardless of vaccination status. Masks should be tight-fitting and cover both the mouth and nose. Read more about UIC’s COVID Safety guidance here.





            Engineering Career Center Hours
          Heading link



 
Copy link








            Drop-in hours for students during the Academic Year	
          

            Monday - Friday, 10am-4pm (first come, first-served basis)
          



            Standard Business Hours	
          

            Monday - Friday, 9am-5pm

          



            Drop-in Hours during Winter Break and Summer	
          

            By Appointment Only

          





            (Excluding University Holidays)

          








